      "span_text": "According to the data of a study involving study subjects from all over the world, the D299G and T399I double mutation haplotype were of high frequency in Caucasians in Europe, and D299G and 399 wildtype can be found in African population; however, no mutations in both D299G and T399I were observed in East Asian countries, including China, Japan, and Korea"
